Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}第七節，第43頁{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Page 43, section 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們需要解釋…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We'd like some clarification...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}第七節對評估工具有所說明…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Section 7 has to do with  the evaluative measures by which...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}「評估工具」{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}"Evaluative measures."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們是在討論成績標準{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What we're talking about here  are performance standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.38,0:00:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}就這麼簡單{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Plain and simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.48,0:00:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不行，會造成更多問題…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We can't have that.  We open that can of worms...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 要拿掉，法蘭  - 總統府希望留著{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Gotta take it out, Frank.  -The Administration wants it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是浪費時間{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Then we're all wasting our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我能減少考試次數{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Now, look, I can cut down  the frequency of testing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 但一定要是全面…  - 這會變得難以收拾{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-but it's got to be a part of the overall...  -That's the thin edge of a 2-ton wedge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 沒得商量  - 等等{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-No way. Non-debatable.  -All right, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}聽他說說也不會怎麼樣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There's no harm in hearing him out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭，你的想法如何？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Frank, what do you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們調整第四條，給我第四條{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We adjust article 4. Hand me article 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}每三年一次，而不是每兩年…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We go every three years instead of two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭，要我們考慮考試…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Frank, for us to even consider testing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.23,0:00:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}馬帝，不能商量時間間隔{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Marty, we can't negotiate time intervals here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我只是說如果可以{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If, I'm just saying if.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}次數間隔不會超過五年{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The frequency could never  be more than five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}五年有點長，但如果你能改善…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Five is a little high.  But if you could bend on that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.61,0:00:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 馬帝  - 等等，不只是次數的問題{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Marty...  -Wait, wait, wait. And it's not just frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}資深教師會得到免稅{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Veteran teachers would have to be exempt
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果他們有優秀教學的證明{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}if they have a proven record  of excellence with the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}請等我一下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}克伊，你主持一下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Corey, will you take the reins on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}是的，第四條關於免稅…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Right, so article 4, in terms of exemptions...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我已經說了多年  我們應該拆除{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I've been saying for years  that we should tear it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}青少年悲劇  郡長譴責議員{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是低俗，也是本郡的恥辱{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's vulgar.  It's an embarrassment to the county.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但法蘭安德沃屢次反對拆除{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But time and time again, Frank Underwood  has fought to keep it standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}要不是他  桃子水塔早就被取代了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If it weren't for him, the Peachoid  would've been replaced ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.47,0:01:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}潔西卡馬斯特斯也會還在人間{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And Jessica Masters would still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}議員必須對這件悲劇做交代{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The Congressman needs  to answer for this tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.47,0:01:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}到底發生了什麼事？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}17歲女孩衝出道路  傳簡訊給她男朋友，我引述{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}A 1 7-year-old girl ran off the road,  texting her boyfriend. And I quote,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}「桃子水塔好像一個大…」  然後車就失控了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}"Doesn't the Peachoid look like a giant..."  And then she lost control of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}老天{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}歐倫在地方媒體大做文章{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Oren's making a big fuss in the local press.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.59,0:01:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他還慫恿父母控告蓋弗尼{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And he's pushing the parents to sue Gaffney.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}控告蓋弗尼？  這是他自己的管轄區{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Sue Gaffney? It's in his own jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}犧牲蓋弗尼再把你拖下水  挺值得的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's worth throwing Gaffney under the bus  to drag you into the mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他又覬覦我的席位  他沒學到教訓嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He's after my seat again.  Has he learned absolutely nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.90,0:01:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是不正當的競選{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's a full-on smear campaign, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 他會毀了你  - 用這個？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-He's out to destroy you.  -With this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這只不過是個桃子  讓他自己出洋相{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's a peach for Christ's sake.  Let him make a fool out of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不會，他會讓你出洋相{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, he will make a fool out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果他能讓全國媒體注意到{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If he spins this right, gets national coverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}全國媒體？這太誇張了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}National coverage? It's a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你就會很慘{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And you will be the butt of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}現在不能旁生枝節{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We can't afford that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你是教育提案的關注焦點{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not when you're in the spotlight  with the Education Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這件事搞得我太多事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This thing has caused me  so much damn trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我知道  - 所以該連絡誰？父母嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I know.  -So who should I call? Parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}打電話不夠，你要親自拜訪{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Phone call's not gonna cut it.  You need to go down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}可以等到週一嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Can it wait until Monday?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}現在處理，就能控制局勢{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We get on this thing right now,  we can contain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果等到週一{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We wait until Monday,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}就無法預料  這個事件的渲染效應{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and there's no way to know  how much this is gonna blow up on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不能去蓋弗尼，工會才剛…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I can't go down to Gaffney.  The unions have just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 能延期  - 他們會很生氣的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-We postpone.  -They're gonna be livid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}馬帝很講道理  他會向他們解釋…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Marty's reasonable, okay?  He will explain to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們就該理所當然接受{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And they're just supposed  to understand and accept
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我得離開協商桌{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}that I had to get up from the negotiating table
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}因為某個二流郡長想…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}because some 2-bit  county administrator wants to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不想打斷你  但這不只是歐倫而已{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't want to interrupt you, sir,  but this is not just about Oren.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}還有父母{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's about the parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你想想這件訴訟{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Now you think about the lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}要是你必須作證怎麼辦？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What happens ifyou have to testify?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}傳票加上作證{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Subpoenas. Depositions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你扯進這件訴訟  教育提案就沒有前途了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You get dragged into a court battle,  there is no Education Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們不能忽視這件事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We can't ignore this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我真的很恨這些小事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I just hate this small ball crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}叫做什麼？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's called the what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 桃子什麼？  - 桃子水塔{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-The peach what?  -The Peachoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}是一座桃子形狀的大水塔{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's a giant water tower  in the shape of a peach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我剛上網查到了，桃子水塔…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Wow. I just googled it. The Peachoid...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她才17歲，琳達{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}She was 17, Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你說得對，我很抱歉{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You're right. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我需要多一周  - 不行{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I need another week.  -That's not gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}總統將在週二演說  我們已經宣佈了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The President makes his speech on Tuesday.  We've already announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}演說可以改期{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Speeches can be rescheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}教育方面得有進展，法蘭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We have to show some progress  on Education, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}百日就快到了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The first 100 days is almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果把演說延期  我們會像在原地打轉{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We push back the speech,  it'll look like we're spinning our wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好吧，我再想辦法  謝謝你，琳達{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}All right. I'll work something out.  Thank you, Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭，這是全國  兩大教育工會的會長{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Frank, these are the heads of the two  largest teachers unions in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我明白{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}週末搭機過來{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}They flew here on a weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}道格會主持  菲利普議員很熟練…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Doug will lead the charge,  Congressman Phillips is well versed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭，他們是來和你見面  你負責這項提案{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}They flew here to see you, Frank.  You're managing this bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}把這個放到另一個袋子裏  我會保持連絡{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Put this in the other bag.  And I'll be in constant communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有大事，就打電話給我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Anything big comes up,  I'm a phone call away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是三百頁的文件  我們需要你坐鎮{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's a 300-page document.  We need you in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我也很想留下  但這是我的戶籍區{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I would stay if I could,  but this is my home district.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}馬帝，幫個忙吧  我們會搞定這件事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Now, Marty, cut me a little slack here.  We'll get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們認識這麼久了  我何時讓你失望過？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You and I go way back.  Have I ever let you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 從來沒有  - 我不想破例{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-No, you haven't.  -And I don't intend to start now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有人嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}新水計劃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 吉莉安？  - 克萊兒{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Gillian?  -Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}真高興終於見到你了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So nice to finally meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我有一點不舒服  我不想害你生病{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm a little under the weather,  I don't want to get you sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 如果你不舒服，我們能…  - 沒關係，只是小感冒{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Well, if you're feeling ill, we can...  -No, no, no. I'm fine. It's just a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 謝謝你來  - 應該的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Well, thank you for coming in.  -Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}到我的辦公室談好嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Shall we talk in my office?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 這些照片很酷  - 謝謝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-These are really cool photographs.  -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}亞當蓋羅威拍攝的  你有聽過他嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Adam Galloway took the pictures.  Have you heard of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒有{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}幾年前我在惠特尼雙年展  認識他的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I met him at the Whitney Biennial  a couple years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我請他拍攝這些照片  他剛在現代美術館辦完展{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and commissioned him to do these.  He just had a big show at PS1.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我對藝術不太瞭解{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm not up to date on the art world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒關係，反正我們也不是  要討論藝術，對嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's all right, we're not here  to talk about photography, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我辦公室在這邊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}My office is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 有問題就找我  - 我能處理{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-You run into any trouble, you call me.  -I got it covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 吉克萊西知道我要來嗎？  - 剛跟他說過{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Gene Clancy know I'm coming?  -Just spoke to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}廢話少說{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}班機訂好了，55分鐘後起飛  愛德會陪你去{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Your flight is booked. Leaves in 55 minutes.  Ed will be joining you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}史提夫呢？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Where's Steve?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他一小時前請病假回家了，議員{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He went home sick about an hour ago, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我來代班  - 你叫什麼名字？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I'll be filling in.  -What's your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 愛德華什麼？  - 米契{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Edward what?  -Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}米契，你開車快嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You drive fast, Meechum?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}華府先驅報{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 你找我嗎？  - 喬伊，進來吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-You wanted to talk to me?  -Come on in, Zoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這位是堤登太太，擁有…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This is Mrs. Tilden, owner of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她知道我是誰{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}She knows who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}堤登太太很喜歡  你的凱薩琳杜倫報導{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Mrs. Tilden liked your profile  on Catherine Durant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我沒有{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我愛死了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有深度又不讓步{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}In-depth. Uncompromising.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}通常我不在出稿前看文章{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Normally I don't read things  before they go to print,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是凱西是我的朋友{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}but Cathy's a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}告訴我你如何事先知道  她會被提名？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Tell me how you knew  she'd be nominated before she did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 你要我的消息來源？  - 湯姆說你不告訴他{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-You want my source?  -Tom says you won't tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我沒告訴過任何人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I haven't told anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我是報社老闆{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, I own the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我很慶幸能在這裏工作{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And I'm very grateful to be working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你也不願意告訴我嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So, you're not gonna tell me either?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你要什麼？  我的消息來源還是職業道德？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Which do you want,  my source or my integrity?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}湯姆{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Tom,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}把喬伊的文章移到週日頭版{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}move Zoe's piece to the front page  of Sunday's edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}讓我再想想{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Let me think that over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你好好地想  想完後把文章放到頭版{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You think it over as much as you want.  Then put it on the front page.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我好不容易  才讓世安站穩腳步{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I've worked really hard  to gain a foothold with WorldWell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}六年前只有我一個人  和一台電腦{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Six years ago it was just me and a MacBook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我明白{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我要兼兩份差才能付房租{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And I had to juggle two temp jobs just  to pay the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是你的寶貝，你不想放手{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's your baby. You don't want to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我只是…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你不用放手，吉莉安{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And you wouldn't have to, Gillian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我只要你繼續經營  你建立起來的事業{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}All I want is for you to grow  what you've already built.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}聽說你解雇了一半的員工{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I heard you fired halfyour staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}對{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這讓我很擔心{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我開除他們  是要騰出空位給你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I let them go to make room for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不確定我們適不適合{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm just not sure we're the right match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}老實說，我有點不太習慣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}To be honest, I'm a little uncomfortable  working with someone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}跟請知名攝影師的人合作{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}who's commissioning famous photographers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}因為我連幫義工買公車票  到辦公室的錢都沒有{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}when I can't even buy my volunteers  bus fare to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}知道妮奇韓慕樂是誰嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do you know who Nikki Hemler is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不知道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}妮奇擁有卻爾西  最大的一間藝廊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Nikki owns one of the biggest galleries  in Chelsea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她很想代表亞當蓋羅威{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}She desperately wanted  to represent Adam Galloway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我把亞當介紹給她{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I delivered on Adam,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}回報是她每年  捐大約四萬元給淨水創權{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and in return she contributes  almost 40 grand a year to CWl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那筆錢能用在影響調查  遊說和研究{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That money goes to impact studies,  lobbying efforts, research.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}世安能從那種錢中受惠  吉莉安{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}WorldWell could benefit from  that sort of money, Gillian,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你的專業也能讓我們受惠{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and we can benefit from your expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我可以考慮嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Can I think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}當然，不用急著決定{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Of course.  We don't have to jump into anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我在這個鄉下地方長大{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I grew up here, in the up-country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}聖經、烤肉，還有斷背山{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Bibles, barbecues and broken backs.
