Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}很高興再見到你  目前情況不是很適合{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Nice to see you again.  I wish it was under better circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 很糟糕，對嗎？  - 真糟糕{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Terrible, isn't it?  -It's just terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你安排得很周到{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This is so thoughtful,  what you've organized here.
