Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 彼得？  - 什麼事？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Hey, Peter?  -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你把燈泡收到哪裏了？  臥房的檯燈壞了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Where do you keep the light bulbs?  The lamp in the bedroom is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在廚房水槽的下面{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}In the kitchen, under the sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是我的想法{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Here's what I think,
