Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我自私，只想到自己{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And I'm being selfish,  and I realize it's mostly about me,
