Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}請不要接受那個工作  克裏絲汀娜{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Please don't take that other job, Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是我的感受{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Anyway, that's how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.92,0:21:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}很高興你告訴我{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm glad you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}特許學校會危及  我們的組織能力，很合理{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Charters jeopardize our ability to organize,  which is reason enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}最大的問題  是比較他們的成功…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But the bigger issue  is that measuring their success against...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}特許學校的評估標準  應該也要一樣…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Charter schools would operate under  the same evaluative standards that every...
