Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.97,0:22:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你不能用同樣的標準來比較{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You can't use the same standards  to compare.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你是說特許學校的標準  要比其他學校{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What, you're advocating  a more demanding criteria
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}更嚴格？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}for charter schools than other schools?
