Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.71,0:22:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}等一下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但我們已經增加  非特許學校的補助一成{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah, but we've already increased  non-charter funding by 10%.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}給特許學校的補助微不足道{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The amount going  to charter schools is negligible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭，重點是慣例  不是數字{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's the precedent, Frank, not the number.
