Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.53,0:22:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有些可以接受，有些不行{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, some of them we can stomach,  some of them we can't.
