Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}來決定補助額…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}to determining the amount of funding  a particular...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.51,0:22:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}想我嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Miss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:22:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}可能有一點{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Maybe a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.11,0:23:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有多久了，15個小時？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What's it been, 15 hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.68,0:23:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}還不夠久到發現你不在了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not even long enough to notice you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}跟馬帝史皮奈拉說{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Tell that to Marty Spinella.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.45,0:23:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 進行得如何？  - 在進行{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-How's it coming?  -It's coming.
