Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.59,0:23:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我在去年秋天種的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I planted them. Last fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.36,0:23:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你沒有吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You did not.
