Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}胡說，我有種過一天花{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not true.  I have gardened exactly one day in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你在史巴登堡做募款活動{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You were down in Spartanburg  doing some sort of fundraiser.
