Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一轉眼，我就跪在土裏{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And next thing you know  I was down on my knees in the dirt,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.42,0:23:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}連蚯蚓都來了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}earthworms and all.
