Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.25,0:24:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你那天見過的《先軀報》記者{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That reporter from The Herald  you met one night.
