Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.78,0:24:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 晚安  - 晚安{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Good night.  -Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.61,0:24:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好的，那樣可以，克伊  馬帝？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah, all right, that's fine, Corey. Marty?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.78,0:24:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭，還有一點解釋要做  問題在這裏{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Frank, had a little bit of explaining to do.  Here's our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.82,0:24:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}解釋？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.72,0:24:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}上次說完之後…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.03,0:24:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你在哪裏？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.43,0:24:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你在做什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.16,0:25:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}下個消息是什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.53,0:25:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}提供給我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.24,0:25:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}南卡羅來納州  地區的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.58,0:25:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}說話方便嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.38,0:25:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}現在不行，有事在忙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.58,0:25:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}還有什麼比我更迫切？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.16,0:25:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒有人可以阻擋你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.59,0:25:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}無法阻擋…  你還沒看我開始呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.30,0:25:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我沒辦法想像{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.20,0:25:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我賭你可以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.64,0:25:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我賭你看過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.72,0:25:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}明天看《起點》  我會給你一個飛吻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.76,0:25:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}法蘭？你在嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Frank? Frank, did we lose you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.06,0:26:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}是的，我在這裏，馬帝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah, I'm here, Marty.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.69,0:26:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們可以兜圈子討論  特許學校的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Look, we can talk ourselves in circles  about charter schools,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.13,0:26:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但我提議…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}but here's what I propose...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.30,0:26:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你在文章裏詳細提到{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}In your profile you go into great detail
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.10,0:26:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}喬伊邦斯採訪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.20,0:26:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}杜倫在早期職業生涯中  遇到性別歧視{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}about the sexism Durant faced  early on in her career.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.80,0:26:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}是的，她首次當選時  參議院還是男人的天下{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's right. When she was first elected,  it was still an old boys' club in the Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.54,0:26:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不久前新聞業也是如此{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Journalism used to be that way too  not so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.41,0:26:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我覺得很幸運{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I feel really lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.08,0:26:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在我之前有很多先軀{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I've had lots of trailblazers come before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.48,0:26:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}比如說，我的同事  珍妮史柯斯基{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}For instance, my colleague, Janine Skorsky,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.32,0:26:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她是《先軀報》首位女性  成為主要政治記者{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}was the first woman at The Herald  to become chief political correspondent.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.89,0:26:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那才是五年前的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And that was only five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.52,0:26:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這些先軀  讓你能發展得這麼快嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Has it been those trailblazers  who've allowed you to rise so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.69,0:26:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你從都會版晉陞到週日頭版{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You've moved up from the metro pages  to the front page Sunday edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.60,0:26:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果珍妮沒有鋪好路{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, I don't know that  that would be possible
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.33,0:26:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我應該沒有可能{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}if Janine hadn't already paved the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.10,0:26:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是否表示  《先軀報》還是很傳統？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So does that mean that The Herald  is not particularly progressive?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.51,0:26:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們很先進{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I think that they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.61,0:26:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}湯姆心胸寬大{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Tom is very open-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.18,0:26:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}是他讓珍妮陞官的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He's the reason Janine got promoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.04,0:26:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那是主編湯姆翰默史密{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's Tom Hammerschmidt,  the executive editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.15,0:26:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 對，我們都叫他「錘子」  - 「錘子」？為什麼？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Yes, we actually call him "The Hammer. "  -"The Hammer"? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.65,0:26:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}因為他很強硬{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Because he's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.98,0:27:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如何強硬？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}How tough?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.12,0:27:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}湯姆的要求很高{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Tom has very high standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.79,0:27:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我很愛他{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.29,0:27:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他是個很棒的良師益友{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He's a great mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.09,0:27:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有時候很令人抓狂{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It can be frustrating at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.06,0:27:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他會要你一而再再而三檢查{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He makes you double  and triple-check things.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.70,0:27:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你一拿到新聞就想發表{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And you want to get the news out  the moment you have it,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.70,0:27:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但他會要你重寫到完美  這就是《先軀報》的精神{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and he makes you rewrite until it's perfect,  but that's what makes The Herald The Herald.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.94,0:27:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在網路時代  這是可行的模式嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Is that a workable model in the Internet age?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.68,0:27:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們的讀者認為如此{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Our readers think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.21,0:27:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你們的讀者人數在下降{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You have a declining readership.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.28,0:27:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但我不覺得是湯姆的責任  那是時勢所趨吧？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I don't lay that at Tom's feet.  I think that that's the times we live in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.58,0:27:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}報社應該順應潮流嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Should newspapers adapt  to the times we live in?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.39,0:27:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}《先軀報》不是不願做調整{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's not that The Herald refuses to adapt.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.36,0:27:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們有網路版{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We have an online presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.06,0:27:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}也許調整得不夠快？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Is that maybe not adapting fast enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.59,0:27:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不會否認{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I wouldn't argue with that statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.16,0:27:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們能做得更多{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We could do more.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.60,0:28:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}今天我們有個特別的客人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We've got a special guest with us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.80,0:28:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他希望今早能有機會  和我們分享幾句話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He asked for the opportunity to share  a few words with us this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.31,0:28:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們的議員，法蘭安德沃{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Our very own Congressman,  Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.46,0:28:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 早安  - 早安{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Good morning.  -Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.03,0:28:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}謝謝你，牧師  還要謝謝唱詩班美麗的歌聲{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Thank you, Reverend. And thanks  to the choir for that beautiful hymn.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.03,0:28:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}今早我想念一段…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I want to read this morning from...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.55,0:29:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不是{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.89,0:29:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你知道大家最不想  討論的話題是什麼嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You know what no one wants to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.36,0:29:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}仇恨{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.06,0:29:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我很瞭解仇恨{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I know all about hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.99,0:29:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}是從你的心底開始{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It starts in your gut. Deep down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.23,0:29:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在那裏蠢蠢欲動，不斷累積{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Where it stirs and churns. And then it rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.60,0:29:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}仇恨會快速累積又猛烈{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hate rises, fast and volcanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.84,0:29:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}然後爆發，烈焰沖天{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It erupts, hot on the breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.27,0:29:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你的眼睛充滿怒火{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Your eyes go wide with fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.68,0:29:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你咬緊牙關  你覺得牙齒會崩裂{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You clench your teeth so hard  you think they'll shatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.08,0:29:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我恨你，老天{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I hate you, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.15,0:29:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我恨你！{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.32,0:29:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}別告訴我你沒說過那樣的話  我知道你有{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Don't tell me you haven't said  those words before. I know you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.13,0:29:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們都說過{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We all have.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.63,0:30:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果你曾痛徹心扉{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If you've ever felt soul-crushing loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.04,0:30:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}今天在座有兩位父母  明白那樣的悲痛{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}There are two parents with us today  who know that pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.68,0:30:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}天下父母最深的痛  就是白髮人送黑髮人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The most terrible hurt of all,  losing a child before her time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.55,0:30:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果狄恩和莉安現在站起來{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If Dean and Leanne were  to stand up right now
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.68,0:30:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}大聲喊出仇恨的言語  我們能責備他們嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and scream those awful words of hate,  could we blame them?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.25,0:30:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不會{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.79,0:30:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}至少我能體會他們的仇恨  我能瞭解{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}At least their hatred I can understand.  I can grasp it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.86,0:30:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是上帝的放縱和殘酷{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But God's wantonness, his cruelty,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.97,0:30:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我無法開始…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I can't even begin to...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.34,0:30:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我的父親在43歲的時候  死於心臟病{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}My father dropped dead of a heart attack  at the age of 43, 43 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.78,0:30:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他過世時  我向上帝說了這些話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And when he died, I looked up to God  and I said those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.65,0:30:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}因為我的父親還那麼年輕  充滿朝氣和夢想{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Because my father was so young,  so full of life, so full of dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.82,0:30:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}為什麼上帝要把他帶走？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Why would God take him from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.79,0:31:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}其實我根本不瞭解他  也不知道他的夢想是什麼{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Truth be told I never really knew him,  or what his dreams were.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.43,0:31:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他很安靜、膽小  幾乎沒有人注意到他{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He was quiet, timid, almost invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.03,0:31:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我的母親看不起他  我的外婆恨他{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}My mother didn't think much of him.  My mother's mother hated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.73,0:31:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一個從沒做過大事的人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The man never scratched the surface of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.07,0:31:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}也許他那麼早過世是好事  他的存在沒有意義{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Maybe it's best he died so young,  he wasn't doing much but taking up space.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.04,0:31:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是這種悼詞  不太有感染力吧？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But that doesn't make for  a very powerful eulogy, now does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.84,0:31:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我擦乾眼淚大喊  「為什麼，上帝？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I wept. I screamed, "Why, God?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.88,0:31:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}「我怎麼能不恨你奪走{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}"How can I not hate you  when you steal from me
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.78,0:31:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}「這世上我最愛也最崇拜的人？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}"the person I most love  and admire in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.72,0:31:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}「我不明白，所以我恨你」{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}"l don't understand it, and I hate you for it."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.20,0:31:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}舊約聖經箴言中說{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}The Bible says in Proverbs,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.97,0:31:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}「全心相信上帝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}"Trust in the Lord with all your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.07,0:31:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}「不要依靠自己的判斷力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}"and lean not on your own understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.28,0:31:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}「不要依靠自己的判斷力」{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}"Lean not on your own understanding."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.08,0:31:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}上帝要我們相信他{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}God is telling us to trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.85,0:32:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}就算我們無知還是要愛他{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}To love him despite our own ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.29,0:32:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}若我們無法忍受  最艱難的考驗就不算信仰了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}After all, what is faith if it doesn't endure  when we are tested the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.80,0:32:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們永遠不會明白  為什麼上帝要帶走潔西卡{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We will never understand  why God took Jessica,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.97,0:32:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}或是我的父親或任何人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}or my father or anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.57,0:32:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}上帝無法給我們答案時  他給了我們愛的能力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And while God may not give us any answers,  he has given us the capacity for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.78,0:32:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們的責任是愛他  而不是質問他的計劃{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Our job is to love him  without questioning his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.42,0:32:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}所以我向禰禱告，親愛的神{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So I pray to you, dear Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.32,0:32:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}請求禰給我們力量  繼續愛禰{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I pray to you to help strengthen  our love for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.46,0:32:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}用禰溫暖的愛  來擁抱狄恩和莉安{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and to embrace Dean and Leanne  with the warmth of your love in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.07,0:32:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我向禰禱告  希望禰能幫我們擊退仇恨{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And I pray that you will help us  fend off hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.97,0:32:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們能真心全意相信禰{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}so that we may all truly trust  in you with all our hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.45,0:33:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不要依靠自己的判斷力{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and lean not on our own understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.59,0:33:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}阿門{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.89,0:33:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}阿門{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.29,0:33:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你的工作是報導新聞  不是製造新聞{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Your job is to the report the news,  not be the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.86,0:33:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我在宣傳報社  - 你是在宣傳喬伊邦斯{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I was promoting the paper.  -You were promoting Zoe Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.63,0:33:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是因為我說  我們叫你「錘子」嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Is this about how I said  we called you "The Hammer"?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.93,0:33:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 如果你不高興，我道歉  - 你沒搞清楚狀況{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Because if that upset you, I apologize.  -You're missing the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.56,0:33:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不希望你跟別人說  我們這裏的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't want you talking about  anything that happens here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.20,0:33:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不要說綽號、我們有多先進  或是我們採用網路{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not nicknames, not how progressive we are,  not whether we're adapting to the lnternet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.37,0:33:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你對這家報社的任何意見  都不要說出去{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Any thoughts you have about this paper  you keep them to yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.94,0:33:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你可以來跟我說{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}or you bring them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.24,0:33:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你不該上電視開始…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You don't get on national television  and start...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.84,0:33:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}抱歉，我不想…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm sorry, I wasn't trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.98,0:33:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不要插嘴{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Don't interrupt when I'm talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.38,0:33:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你能像大人一樣跟我說話  湯姆{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You can speak to me like an adult, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.48,0:33:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不用像在跟小女孩說教一樣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You don't have to lecture me like a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.28,0:33:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你還沒有到大人的地步{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You haven't earned the right  to be treated as an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.09,0:33:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你以為幾篇頭版新聞  還有電視專訪{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You think a few front page stories  and some face time on TV
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.32,0:33:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}就能讓你成為  下一個朱蒂米勒？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}makes you the next Judy Miller?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.59,0:33:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你還有很長一段路要走  不要太囂張{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You've got a long way to go.  Don't be so arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.40,0:33:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你覺得女人要求你尊敬她  表示她很囂張？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Okay, so you think when a woman asks  to be treated with respect, that's arrogance?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.23,0:33:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你是說我有性別歧視？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Are you accusing me of sexism?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.80,0:34:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}只不過是聊天而已{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Just making an observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.97,0:34:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不准上電視一個月{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No TV for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.24,0:34:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 什麼？  - 你聽到了，不准接專訪{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-What?  -You heard me. No interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.54,0:34:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 這真的很不公平  - 你要永遠都不能上電視嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-That's completely unfair.  -You want to make it no TV indefinitely?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.28,0:34:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒事了，你可以走了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We're done. You can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.34,0:34:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}喂？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.15,0:34:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}吉莉安，我是克萊兒安德沃  我能上來嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Gillian, it's Claire Underwood.  Can I come up?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.19,0:34:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你有看醫生嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Have you seen a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.79,0:34:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}腸胃炎沒那麼嚴重  大概再一周就沒事了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Giardia's not so bad.  It'll pass in another week or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.30,0:35:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 你沒有健保嗎？  - 沒有{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-You don't have health insurance, do you?  -Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.03,0:35:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我會幫你預約我的私人醫生  明天幫你看看{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'll make an appointment for you  to see my personal GP tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.37,0:35:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}吃藥沒什麼用  讓病自然過了就好了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Medicine doesn't really do much.  You have to let it run its course.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.11,0:35:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們會在適當的監督下  讓病自然好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, we'll let it run its course  under proper supervision.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.78,0:35:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 不要再拒絕了  - 克萊兒…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I won't take no for an answer on this.  -Claire...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.21,0:35:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果有必要  我會親自把你拖到醫院{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'll drag you to the hospital myself  if I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.45,0:35:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你要看醫生，不要再跟我吵了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You're going to the doctor. No argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.52,0:35:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}謝謝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.06,0:35:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們要走了  完全聽不進我說的話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}They're about to walk.  They won't listen to a word I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.09,0:35:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 兩個工會都一樣？  - 對{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Both unions?  -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.73,0:35:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}叫馬帝聽電話{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Put Marty on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.93,0:35:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}等一下，馬帝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Hang on. Marty.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.70,0:35:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好，法蘭嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yeah. It's Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.27,0:35:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這招沒用，法蘭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This isn't working, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.74,0:35:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}馬帝，你必須把他們留在裏面{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Marty, you have got  to keep them in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.51,0:35:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們失去耐性了  他們很不高興你不在，法蘭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}They lost their patience, all right?  They're upset you're not in the room, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.94,0:35:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 我今天下午會回來  - 太遲了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-I'll be back this afternoon.  -No. It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.71,0:35:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}跟他們說我會過來  說明特許學校補助的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Look, tell them I'll come down  on subsidies for charter schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.68,0:35:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}就算如此  他們還是不喜歡成績標準{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Even so, they're angry  about the performance standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.75,0:35:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這件事八字還沒一撇  還有很多要做…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We're not even halfway through this thing.  There's so much in it that they...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.59,0:36:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那跟他們說我能調整成績標準  每五年一次{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Then tell them that I'll roll over on  performance standards. Five-year intervals.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.63,0:36:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你應該親自說，法蘭{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It should be you telling them that, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.93,0:36:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在這個會議室{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You, here at this table.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.30,0:36:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我知道，我盡力而為，馬帝{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I know that.  You know, I'm doing the best I can, Marty.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.33,0:36:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是我分身乏術{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I can't be in two places at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.30,0:36:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}聽著，我向你保證  如果你能讓他們待在裏面{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Now look, I promise you,  if you keep them in that room,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.07,0:36:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我回去後會很快解決這件事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}we will get through this hump  as soon as I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.84,0:36:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}馬帝，你是他們的陳情代表  你知道什麼對他們最好{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Marty, you are their lobbyist.  You know what's best for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.08,0:36:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}幫幫他們吧{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Save them from themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.22,0:36:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好吧，我盡量試試{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Okay. I'll see what I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.16,0:36:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我是史坦普{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It's Stamper.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.36,0:36:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不要讓史皮奈拉離開你的視線{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Do not let Spinella out of your sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.59,0:36:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}必要時把門鎖起來{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And lock the goddamn doors if you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.10,0:36:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}瞭解{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.73,0:36:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.17,0:36:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我知道你是大忙人  希望沒有耽擱你…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I know you're a busy man,  I hope we're not keeping you...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.47,0:36:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒有，我時間多得很{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, no, no. I've got all the time in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.61,0:36:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是火腿，這些是火雞  還有馬鈴薯沙拉{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}This is ham and these are turkey.  And there's some potato salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.94,0:36:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}禱告好嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Shall we have a prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.25,0:36:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}親愛的上帝…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Gracious loving God...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.98,0:36:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 你得過這種病嗎？  - 第三次了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-Have you had this before?  -This is the third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.82,0:37:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我已經習慣了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm used to it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.29,0:37:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不是很習慣  但是比瘧疾厲害{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, I'm not used to it, but it beats malaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.59,0:37:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你得過瘧疾？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You've had malaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.99,0:37:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在辛巴威的時候病了一個月{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}In Zimbabwe. That took me out for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.86,0:37:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你犧牲很大{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You make a lot of sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.10,0:37:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不覺得是犧牲{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I don't see it as a sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.00,0:37:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你為了創辦非營利機構  拒絕谷歌六位數薪水的工作{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You turned down a six-figure salary  at Google to start your own non-profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.37,0:37:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}在帕羅奧多市不會有瘧疾{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}People don't get malaria in Palo Alto.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.61,0:37:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你有做功課{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You do your research.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.27,0:37:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果是我關心的人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}When it's someone I care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.11,0:37:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}克萊兒，我拒絕那份工作  因為我不想恨自己{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Claire, I turned down that job  because I would've hated myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.05,0:37:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}薪水很好，但是又如何？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}It was a lot of money, but for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.09,0:37:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們就能滿足  人種多樣性的配額{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So they could fill their diversity quota
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.09,0:37:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}一個有史丹佛學歷的亞洲女生？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}with an Asian girl  peddling a Stanford degree?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.16,0:37:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不是隨便的亞洲女生  是學生代表{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not just any Asian girl. A valedictorian.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.86,0:37:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}讓我給你谷歌不能給你的東西{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Let me offer you what Google couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.90,0:37:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我明白集能力  美麗和野心於一身的滋味{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I know what it is to be capable  and beautiful and ambitious,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.20,0:37:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}還有像謝吉和賴瑞擁有{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and be on people like Sergey  and Larry's checklist
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.84,0:37:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那些很有面子的戰利品{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}of things that look good to have on a shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.28,0:37:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我不是在招攬你{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm not trying to acquisition you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.85,0:38:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你是一位讓我佩服的女性  這很難得{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What I see in you is a woman I admire,  which doesn't happen often.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.49,0:38:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我希望能幫你  我想幫你排除萬難{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I want to enable you.  I want to clear the way for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.92,0:38:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好讓你能達到  你想要完成的目標{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}So that you can achieve what you want  to achieve, on your own terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.40,0:38:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}謝謝你請我喝茶{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Thanks for the tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.47,0:38:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我明天會派車去接你看醫生{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And I will send a car to pick you up  for the doctor tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.24,0:38:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}等你好了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}When you're back on your feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.34,0:38:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你覺得我們可能繼續嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}do you think maybe  we can work something out?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.91,0:38:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}是的，我覺得可以{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Yes, I think we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.85,0:38:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是她在高三時的舞會{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's her at junior prom.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.02,0:38:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}好漂亮{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.09,0:38:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是她穿皮夾克的時候{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Here she is in her letter-jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.53,0:38:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她高一就進了校隊{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}She made varsity as a freshman.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.83,0:38:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我記得她得知消息的那天{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I remember the day she found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.83,0:38:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}教練打電話來  潔西興奮的不得了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Coach called,  and Jessie starts jumping up and down,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.17,0:39:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}「媽，你知道嗎？」{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}"Mom, guess what?"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.15,0:39:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我很抱歉{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.25,0:39:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}別道歉，沒關係{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Don't be. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.62,0:39:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}為什麼要這樣？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Why are we doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.09,0:39:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}老實說  舊事重提有什麼意義？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Honestly. What's to be gained  dredging up all this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.59,0:39:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}有時回憶好事會有幫助{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Remembering the good things  helps sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.56,0:39:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}讓我的太太流淚時沒有幫助{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Not when it puts my wife in tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.93,0:39:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我很感謝你在教堂裏說的話  但是對我們沒有用{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I appreciate what you said at the church,  but it doesn't do us any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.73,0:39:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這也沒有用{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Neither does this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.17,0:39:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}那我能幫到什麼？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, what can I do to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.74,0:39:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}什麼都不行{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.27,0:39:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}她不在了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.14,0:39:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}沒錯，我不能改變事實{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You're right. I can't change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.61,0:39:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但是我可以保證市政府  賠償你們一大筆錢{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But I can make sure the city offers you  a sizable settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.18,0:39:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你是說收買我們？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}You mean buy us off?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.85,0:39:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}不是，我是說能幫你們  避免多年的官司{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}No, I mean help you avoiding  years of court battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.85,0:39:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}潔西卡本來要上弗曼大學  對嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Jessica was gonna go to Furman,  is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.92,0:39:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}- 排球獎學金？  - 對，全額獎學金{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}-On a volleyball scholarship?  -Yes, a full ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.36,0:39:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我今早跟大學校長談過了{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Well, I spoke to the president  of the university this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.63,0:39:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們想以你女兒的名義  創辦一個新獎學金{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}and we'd like to create a new scholarship  in your daughter's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.93,0:40:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果你們同意的話  由你們決定{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If you'd like that. It's entirely up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.27,0:40:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}但最重要的是我們必須保證  這樣的事不會再發生{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}But most importantly we have to make sure  that this never happens again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.64,0:40:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我們已經架好安全告示牌{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}We've got safety billboards going up,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.77,0:40:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}晚上停止打燈照水塔  還有把護欄建好…{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}stopped lighting the tower at night,  and we're putting the guardrails in...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.78,0:40:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這些應該在她衝出道路前  就該做好的{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Should've done all that  before she ran off the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.48,0:40:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}馬斯特斯先生  你希望我辭職嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Would you like me to resign, Mr. Masters?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.98,0:40:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}只要你說一聲，我就會下台{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Just say the word and it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.82,0:40:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}如果這會帶給你慰藉{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}If it will bring you any satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.60,0:40:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}我問過牧師一次{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}I asked the reverend once,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.50,0:40:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}「我們該怎麼面對  這種失去感覺的痛苦？」{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}"What are we supposed to do  in the face of so much senseless pain?"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.04,0:40:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他跟我說{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And he said to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.41,0:40:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}「我們還能做什麼{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}"What else can we do
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.88,0:40:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}「只能將這沒有意義的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}"but take what seems meaningless,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.95,0:40:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}「轉變成有意義的事？」{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}"and try to make something  meaningful from it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.92,0:40:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他沒有錯{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.72,0:40:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}這是上帝透過我們幫助人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}That's how God works through us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.22,0:41:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你會讓我幫你嗎？{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Will you let me work for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.63,0:41:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}你必須瞭解我的市民{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}What you have to understand  about my people
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.87,0:41:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們都是好人{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}is that they are a noble people.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.97,0:41:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}謙虛是他們的自豪  這是優點，也是弱點{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Humility is their form of pride.  It is their strength. It is their weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.68,0:41:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}只要你能在他們面前  低聲下氣{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}And ifyou can humble yourself before them,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.91,0:41:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}他們會為你做任何事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}they will do anything you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.25,0:41:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs24}告訴我們獎學金的事{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs12}Tell us more about the scholarship.
